name: WKExtendedRuntimeSessionInvalidationReason
desc: The reasons why a session can become invalid.

items.name: case error
items.desc: An error prevented the session from running.

items.name: case sessionInProgress
items.desc: This app already has a running session.

items.name: case expired
items.desc: The session used all of its allocated time.

items.name: case resignedFrontmost
items.desc: The app lost its frontmost status.
